OL,5, Extremists are using mainstream video  
OL,6, games and gaming chat platforms to     
OL,7, spread hate, BBC Click has found.      
OL,9,FOver three months, researchers found   
OL,10,Fanti-Semitism, racism and homophobia on
OL,11,Fplatforms, including DLive and Odysee, 
OL,12,Fwhere users stream and chat about games
OL,13,Fsuch as Call of Duty and Minecraft.    
OL,15,FCampaigners say including extremist    
OL,16,Fnarratives among everyday conversations
OL,17,Fcan be a pathway to radicalisation.    
OL,19,FThese conversations then move to spaces
OL,20,Fsuch as private Telegram channels.     
